{
  "texts": [
    "Following this five-dimensional classification, we have provided a systematic overview of use cases, objectives, targeted audiences and main types of questions addressed by existing dialoguebased xAI systems.",
    "Most importantly, we have identified theoretical frameworks that can be used to define the type of dialogue carried out by the system, and we have presented a general meta-level architecture and core components for the implementation of dialoguebased xAI systems.",
    "Finally, we have highlighted shortcomings of current systems that can be addressed in future work.",
    "Our review focused on publications from the ACM Digital Library, Scopus, and the IEEE libraries.",
    "While this selection encompasses a considerable range of high-quality databases, it carries the limitation of possibly overlooking pertinent information from non-peer-reviewed sources and other databases."
  ]
}